01:45:06.651 --> 01:45:08.362
Leave me alone!

1297
01:45:10.114 --> 01:45:12.615
Now, we know that can
never happen now, don't we?


1298
01:45:12.657 --> 01:45:15.327
How would we
ever get along in this world


1299
01:45:15.369 --> 01:45:17.288
if it weren't for me?

1300
01:45:34.763 --> 01:45:36.223
Let's play our game?

1301
01:45:36.265 --> 01:45:38.142
Not now, Adam.

1302
01:45:38.183 --> 01:45:40.311
Come on, please?

1303
01:45:44.482 --> 01:45:46.191
You be Margaret.

1304
01:45:48.277 --> 01:45:49.903
I'm the survivor.

1305
01:45:49.945 --> 01:45:52.490
I'm the one who
got us through hell!


1306
01:45:52.531 --> 01:45:54.908
And this whore
just thinks she can


1307
01:45:54.950 --> 01:45:57.578
