1308
01:45:57.620 --> 01:45:59.330
Because of love?

1309
01:45:59.371 --> 01:46:01.957
Shut up! Shut up! Shut up!

1310
01:46:01.999 --> 01:46:06.669
- This isn't love.
- Shut up!


1311
01:46:06.711 --> 01:46:08.839
All people want to do

1312
01:46:08.880 --> 01:46:10.966
is use you!

1313
01:46:11.008 --> 01:46:14.094
Eat you up and
spit you out, Grace!


1314
01:46:14.136 --> 01:46:17.264
Until there is
nothing left of you!


1315
01:46:17.306 --> 01:46:18.807
That's not true!

1316
01:46:18.849 --> 01:46:21.393
We have to
make her go away, Grace!


1317
01:46:21.435 --> 01:46:22.978
No, please!

1318
01:46:23.020 --> 01:46:24.771
Leave me alone!

1319
01:46:24.813 --> 01:46:27.232
No, the bitch must die!

1320
01:46:27.274 --> 01:46:28.984
No, this is wrong!

1321
01:46:29.026 --> 01:46:30.569
Kill her! Kill her!

1322
01:46:30.611 --> 01:46:32.863
I said stop!

1323
01:46:40.329 --> 01:46:43.457
Grace! Grace, Grace.

1324
01:46:43.499 --> 01:46:44.707
Grace?

1325
01:46:44.749 --> 01:46:46.709
Mary...

1326
01:46:48.212 --> 01:46:50.214
I'm sorry.

1327
01:46:53.258 --> 01:46:54.926
Please don't give up on me.

1328
01:46:56.094 --> 01:46:57.388
I won't.

1329
01:46:57.429 --> 01:46:59.557
I love you, Mary.

1330
01:47:01.141 --> 01:47:03.561
I love you, too, sweet girl.

1331
01:48:07.750 --> 01:48:10.252
Working on a new book
in the series, Ms. Morrison?


1332
01:48:10.294 --> 01:48:12.837
Actually, no, I'm
doing something different


1333
01:48:12.879 --> 01:48:15.257
that I've been
wanting to do for a long time.


1334
01:48:16.508 --> 01:48:17.718
Bye.

1335
01:48:18.761 --> 01:48:19.970
Bye.

1336
01:48:25.517 --> 01:48:26.893
I did it.

1337
01:48:29.480 --> 01:48:32.566
All I needed was to
get my ass kicked out the door.


1338
01:48:34.359 --> 01:48:35.653
It's all for you.

1339
01:49:00.803 --> 01:49:02.012
Hi.

1340
01:49:42.845 --> 01:49:44.471
Deal me in.

1341
01:49:44.513 --> 01:49:46.640
Mary!

1342
01:49:47.974 --> 01:49:49.309
Mm, I've missed you!

1343
01:49:49.351 --> 01:49:51.395
Aw, I've missed you, too.

1344
01:49:51.436 --> 01:49:53.271
I have something for you.

1345
01:49:56.899 --> 01:49:58.819
Ta-da!

1346
01:49:58.861 --> 01:50:00.945
Oh, you're the best!

1347
01:50:00.987 --> 01:50:02.531
Simply the best!

1348
01:50:02.573 --> 01:50:04.408
- Thank you!
- You're welcome!


1349
01:50:04.449 --> 01:50:05.868
What are we gonna play?

1350
01:50:05.908 --> 01:50:07.369
Um, Crazy Eights.

1351
01:50:07.411 --> 01:50:08.871
Okay!

1352
01:50:13.958 --> 01:50:16.670
Four, five,

1353
